Important Notice
----------------

Your moderator has moved to the San Francisco Bay Area.  Please send all
postal correspondence to Shadow Island's new address.  If you have recently
sent mail to the old address, don't worry, it will be collected and
forwarded.  However, please be tolerant of any delays the forwarding may
incur.

Our new address is:

	Shadow Island Games
	P.O. Box 390983
	Mountain View, CA 94039-0983

Electronic contact information (domain name, email address, web URL's, etc.)
will not change.

Our phone and fax numbers will change at some point in the future.
You may continue to use the existing numbers for now.


